sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client
    participant API as GET /api/building-polygon
    participant OSM as OpenStreetMap Nominatim

    Client ->> API: GET /api/building-polygon?lat=51.1&lng=4.4
    activate API

    API ->> API: Validate lat, lng query params

    alt Missing lat or lng
        API -->> Client: 400 { error: 'Missing lat/lng' }
    else Valid coordinates
        API ->> OSM: GET /reverse?format=jsonv2<br/>&lat=51.1&lon=4.4<br/>&polygon_geojson=1&zoom=18
        activate OSM

        Note over API,OSM: User-Agent: 'DakOppervlakte/1.0'

        OSM -->> API: { geojson: { type, coordinates } }
        deactivate OSM

        alt GeoJSON type is Polygon
            API -->> Client: 200 { type: 'Feature',<br/>geometry: { type: 'Polygon', coordinates } }

        else GeoJSON type is Point (no building outline)
            API ->> API: Generate 10x10m fallback square<br/>(±5-6m offset from center)
            API -->> Client: 200 { type: 'Feature',<br/>geometry: { type: 'Polygon', coordinates: [square] } }

        else No geojson in response
            API -->> Client: 200 { features: [],<br/>debug: { lat, lng, msg: 'No building found...' } }
        end
    end
    deactivate API
